rated\njugular venous dynamics consistent with invasive central venous monitoring\nduring three protocols that altered central venous pressure. This system\nprovides non-invasive monitoring of pressure-induced jugular venous dynamics in\nclinically relevant conditions where catheterization is traditionally required,\nenabling monitoring in non-surgical environments.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 22 Jul 2020 16:38:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 6 Nov 2020 20:54:09 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 24 Mar 2021 11:02:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-25"}
