d from the superconducting transition\ntemperature of elemental lead (Pb). As a result of these data and analysis we\npropose a practical algorithm to infer the evolution of pressure with\ntemperature in a piston-cylinder cell.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 22 Jul 2020 22:22:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-24"}
