is for memory implementation. Therefore, the skewed CPR of 3D\nnano-SQUID enables further superconducting memory cell miniaturization by\novercoming the inductance limitation of the loop area.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 Jul 2020 01:05:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-30"}
