elieve that this work, by its generality, establishes\nbridges interesting to explore between optimal control problems of ODEs with a\nharvesting term and their PDE counterpart.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 Jul 2020 04:51:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-24"}
