ale detects a large number of malicious actors on top of hard-coded rules and\ncontent classifiers, increasing the total recall by 89% over those approaches\nalone.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 Jul 2020 13:25:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-24"}
