del on a triangular lattice\nin the flat band limit. Our results demonstrate that two-dimensional\nsemiconductor moir\\'e superlattices are a highly tunable platform to study the\nstripe phases and their interplay with other symmetry breaking ground states.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 Jul 2020 15:28:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 28 Jul 2020 15:52:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-21"}
